smacksutil.configsceren.title: SmacksUtil
text.autoconfig.smacksutil.option.maxRen: Allows the player to define how many Blocks can be rendered. This is used to reduce lag.
text.autoconfig.smacksutil.option.maxSha: Allows the player to define the max Shapeless Radius.
text.autoconfig.smacksutil.option.maxRen: Max Render Radius in Shapeless Mode
Allows the player to define the max Shapeless Radius. If current radius > max radius rendering is stopped.
text.autoconfig.smacksutil.option.enable: Allows the player to enable/disable Shapeless Vertical Mode.
text.autoconfig.smacksutil.option.maxSha: Max Radius in Shapeless Vertical Mode
Allows the player to define the max Shapeless Vertical Radius.
text.autoconfig.smacksutil.option.maxRen: Allows the player to define the max Shapeless Vertical Radius. If current radius > max radius rendering is stopped..
